name: BLACK GLOW IN THE DARK LOGO T-SHIRT
description:
A lot of you have asked for it, so instead of just offering the White on White Glow in the Dark Logo T-Shirt, we now have it in Black as well!

I know that Glow in the Dark could be a little cheesy, but it's actually pretty freakin cool!

Prepare to make an unforgettable fashion statement with the lights off!

Heavyweight 100% Cotton T-Shirt. Fabric is 6.1oz heavyweight, pre-shrunk cotton. Classic T-Shirt cut.

Payment is processed through paypal, but if you do not have an account, you can simply pay with your credit card!

Please allow up to 7 days for your order to be processed packed and shipped via USPS. Your order confirmation will be a paypal email that is automatically generated.

Shipment within the United States is USPS and paypal will send out a tracking number as soon as the item ships.

International shipment is sent via USPS First Class International and should arrive within 10-15 days after your order is shipped, but may take a little longer depending on customs.

USPS does not offer a tracking numbers for First Class Mail. If you have any questions about your order use the contact form or email me Andy@unknownphotographer.net
